    <head>
  <title><%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> – Marketing Tools for Service Businesses</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <style>
    /* ========= <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> Marketing Tools Page ========= */

    .mkt-page {
      --bg: #f5f5fb;
      --bg-card: #ffffff;
      --text-main: #111827;
      --text-sub: #4b5563;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --border-soft: #e5e7eb;
      --accent: #4f46e5;
      --accent-soft: #eef2ff;
      --accent-dark: #312e81;
      --accent-green: #16a34a;
      --shadow-soft: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      --radius-lg: 18px;
      --radius-md: 14px;
      --radius-pill: 999px;

      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text-main);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #eef2ff 0, #f9fafb 40%, #f3f4f6 100%);
      padding: 40px 16px 72px;
    }

    .mkt-page * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .mkt-shell {
      max-width: 1120px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ---------- Hero ---------- */

    .mkt-hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .mkt-hero {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .mkt-kicker {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.5);
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff, #eef2ff);
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.09em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .mkt-kicker-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #a5b4fc 0, #4f46e5 55%, #1e1b4b 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.9);
    }

    .mkt-title {
      font-size: clamp(32px, 4.2vw, 40px);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .mkt-title span {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .mkt-sub {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      max-width: 520px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .mkt-hero-note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .mkt-cta-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .btn-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: transform 0.12s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), #6366f1);
      color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.4);
      border-color: rgba(191, 219, 254, 0.9);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 38px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.6);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: #ffffff;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.6);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #f3f4ff;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .mkt-hero-foot {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .mkt-hero-foot span {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .mkt-hero-media {
      position: relative;
    }

    .mkt-hero-card {
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.25), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.98));
      padding: 18px 18px 20px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .mkt-hero-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .mkt-hero-chip {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.5);
    }

    .mkt-hero-status {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.18);
      border: 1px solid rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.7);
      color: #bbf7d0;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .mkt-hero-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .mkt-hero-stat label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .mkt-hero-stat strong {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .mkt-campaign-list {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .mkt-campaign-list ul {
      padding-left: 16px;
    }

    .mkt-campaign-list li {
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .mkt-hero-footer {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .mkt-hero-footer span {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .mkt-hero-footer-dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #22c55e;
      box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.9);
    }

    .mkt-hero-shadow {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 18px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* ---------- Intro ---------- */

    .mkt-intro {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .mkt-intro h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .mkt-intro p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .mkt-intro strong {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ---------- Feature grid ---------- */

    .mkt-feature-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .mkt-feature-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .mkt-feature-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .mkt-feature-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.03);
      padding: 18px 18px 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .mkt-feature-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .mkt-feature-title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .mkt-feature-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .mkt-feature-meta {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    /* ---------- Two-column sections ---------- */

    .mkt-section-block {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 36px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 44px;
    }

    .mkt-section-block.reverse {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1.2fr);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .mkt-section-block,
      .mkt-section-block.reverse {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .mkt-section-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .mkt-section-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .mkt-section-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .mkt-section-text + .mkt-section-text {
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .mkt-section-list {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      padding-left: 18px;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .mkt-section-list li {
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .mkt-section-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      padding: 18px 18px 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .mkt-section-card h3 {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .mkt-section-card p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .mkt-pill-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .mkt-pill {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      font-size: 11px;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .mkt-pill.alt {
      background: #ecfdf5;
      color: #166534;
    }

    /* ---------- Testimonials ---------- */

    .mkt-section-header {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .mkt-section-kicker {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .mkt-section-main-title {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .mkt-section-sub {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      max-width: 560px;
    }

    .mkt-testimonial-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 52px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .mkt-testimonial-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .mkt-testimonial-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .mkt-testimonial-card {
      background: #0b1020;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: 18px 18px 16px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
    }

    .mkt-testimonial-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.5), transparent 55%);
      opacity: 0.9;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .mkt-testimonial-logo {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .mkt-testimonial-heading {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .mkt-testimonial-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #cbd5f5;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .mkt-testimonial-person {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .mkt-testimonial-person strong {
      display: block;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    /* ---------- Articles ---------- */

    .mkt-articles-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .mkt-articles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .mkt-articles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .mkt-article-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      padding: 14px 14px 16px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
    }

    .mkt-article-tag {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .mkt-article-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .mkt-article-text {
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .mkt-article-meta {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .mkt-article-link {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .mkt-article-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* ---------- Newsletter ---------- */

    .mkt-newsletter {
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #111827, #020617);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .mkt-newsletter {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .mkt-newsletter h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .mkt-newsletter p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .mkt-newsletter-form {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .mkt-newsletter-input {
      flex: 1 1 180px;
      min-width: 0;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.7);
      padding: 8px 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      outline: none;
    }

    .mkt-newsletter-input::placeholder {
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    .mkt-newsletter-btn {
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: none;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), #6366f1);
      color: #f9fafb;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.5);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .mkt-newsletter-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<%= render partial: "layouts/header" %>
<div class="mkt-page" id="marketing-tools">
  <div class="mkt-shell">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="mkt-hero">
      <div>
        <h1 class="mkt-title">
          Turn <span>happy customers</span> into your best marketing channel.
        </h1>
        <p class="mkt-sub">
          <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> Marketing Tools help you stay in touch with the right customers at the right time –
          with simple campaigns, upsell offers and reminders that run alongside your schedule.
        </p>
        <p class="mkt-hero-note">
          Start small with basic follow-up messages, then grow into fully targeted campaigns as your
          customer list expands.
        </p>

        <div class="mkt-cta-row">
          <a href="/users/sign_up" class="btn-pill btn-primary">Start a free trial</a>
          <a href="/pricing" class="btn-pill btn-secondary">See pricing</a>
        </div>
        <p class="mkt-hero-foot">
          <span>All driven by your existing <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> data.</span> No extra spreadsheets or imports.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: campaign mockup -->
      <div class="mkt-hero-media">
        <div class="mkt-hero-card">
          <div class="mkt-hero-header">
            <div class="mkt-hero-chip"><%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> · Campaigns</div>
            <div class="mkt-hero-status">Campaign live</div>
          </div>

          <div class="mkt-hero-stats">
            <div class="mkt-hero-stat">
              <label>Opened</label>
              <strong>78%</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-hero-stat">
              <label>Booked</label>
              <strong>43</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-hero-stat">
              <label>Revenue</label>
              <strong>$6.3k</strong>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mkt-campaign-list">
            <strong>Segment:</strong>
            <ul>
              <li>Customers not visited in the last 90 days</li>
              <li>With at least 2 past jobs</li>
              <li>Within 10 miles of your current routes</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="mkt-hero-footer">
            <span>
              <span class="mkt-hero-footer-dot"></span>
              Sent via SMS &amp; email
            </span>
            <span>Personalised with names &amp; addresses</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mkt-hero-shadow"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- INTRO -->
    <section class="mkt-intro">
      <h2>Simple tools to stay visible between visits.</h2>
      <p>
        You already have a valuable asset: a list of customers who trust you. <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> helps you
        reach them with offers, updates and reminders based on real activity – not guesswork.
      </p>
      <p>
        Use customer tags, routes, services and last-visit dates to build powerful yet easy-to-understand
        segments. Then send targeted campaigns that feel personal and relevant, not spammy.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>All from the same place you run your jobs.</strong> No exporting data or juggling multiple tools.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- FEATURE GRID -->
    <section class="mkt-feature-grid">
      <article class="mkt-feature-card">
        <p class="mkt-feature-label">Customer Segments</p>
        <h3 class="mkt-feature-title">Target the right people in a few clicks</h3>
        <p class="mkt-feature-text">
          Build lists using location, services, tags, last visit date, spending and more. Save your
          favourite segments so they’re ready next time you want to fill gaps in the schedule.
        </p>
        <p class="mkt-feature-meta">
          Example: “Customers with gutter cleaning last autumn within 5 miles of Route 3”.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="mkt-feature-card">
        <p class="mkt-feature-label">Email &amp; SMS</p>
        <h3 class="mkt-feature-title">Send campaigns using the channels customers prefer</h3>
        <p class="mkt-feature-text">
          Choose email, SMS or both for each campaign depending on how urgent the message is and how your
          customers like to hear from you.
        </p>
        <p class="mkt-feature-meta">
          Replies land back in your <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> inbox, not someone’s personal phone.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="mkt-feature-card">
        <p class="mkt-feature-label">Templates</p>
        <h3 class="mkt-feature-title">Create templates once, re-use forever</h3>
        <p class="mkt-feature-text">
          Save your best-performing offers as templates. Insert tokens such as customer name, next visit,
          service or balance to keep every message personalised.
        </p>
        <p class="mkt-feature-meta">
          Handy for seasonal campaigns like spring cleans or end-of-year check-ups.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="mkt-feature-card">
        <p class="mkt-feature-label">Upsells</p>
        <h3 class="mkt-feature-title">Offer add-ons at the perfect moment</h3>
        <p class="mkt-feature-text">
          Use completed-job data to follow up with related services. For example, promote gutter guards
          to customers who recently had their gutters cleaned.
        </p>
        <p class="mkt-feature-meta">
          Turn one-off jobs into long-term relationships.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="mkt-feature-card">
        <p class="mkt-feature-label">Win-back Campaigns</p>
        <h3 class="mkt-feature-title">Bring back customers you haven’t seen in a while</h3>
        <p class="mkt-feature-text">
          Automatically identify customers who haven’t booked for months and send tailored offers to win
          them back – without blasting your whole list.
        </p>
        <p class="mkt-feature-meta">
          A quiet week becomes an opportunity instead of a problem.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="mkt-feature-card">
        <p class="mkt-feature-label">Measurement</p>
        <h3 class="mkt-feature-title">See exactly what each campaign delivers</h3>
        <p class="mkt-feature-text">
          Track opens, clicks and – crucially – jobs booked and revenue generated. Learn what works so
          every campaign gets a little better.
        </p>
        <p class="mkt-feature-meta">
          Understand marketing impact in terms your team cares about: jobs and cash.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <!-- DEEPER FEATURES -->
    <section>

      <!-- Marketing + Portal -->
      <article class="mkt-section-block">
        <div>
          <p class="mkt-section-label">Portal + Marketing</p>
          <h2 class="mkt-section-title">Turn your portal into a quiet marketing engine.</h2>
          <p class="mkt-section-text">
            Because marketing tools are built on top of your <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> Customer Portal and messaging, it’s
            easy to invite customers back to self-service: booking new work, accepting quotes or paying balances.
          </p>
          <p class="mkt-section-text">
            Use short links in SMS and email that take customers directly to the actions you want them to
            complete – no complex landing pages required.
          </p>
